When first published, the novel was on The New York Times Best Seller list for two years and generally received well by critics. With its positive reception, Barack Obama put it on his summer reading list and the book was optioned for adaptations.', NULL, 2011, '8498383765', '9788498383768', 640, NULL, 1434, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/8474220-L.jpg', '/works/OL14933038W', NULL, 'Jun 07, 2011', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'cutting-for-stone-abraham-verghese', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 05:42:29', '2026-03-24 23:24:42');
